Mid Level / Flinching=
Flinching the Kalphite Queen is a slower method than conventional methods, however it requires much fewer resources per kill, allowing even low level players to do extended trips of 5 or more kills. This method is more easily employed by ironman players, as due to the Kalphite Queen's lair being instanced, they can leave and re-enter the instance to reset all the spawns, making it much quicker to set things up again.

Due to the slow nature of flinching, it is highly recommended to have a Kalphite [[Slayer task]], as the [[Slayer helmet]] can give very large bonuses. [[Verac the Defiled's equipment]] can hit through the Queen's high defences on both phases incredibly well even without a slayer task. Otherwise, the [[Zombie axe]] or [[Keris partisan of breaching]] have the highest expected hits for both phases.
