High Level / Resetting=
*A [[Dragon warhammer]] or [[Elder maul]] is important for lowering Kalphite Queen's defence if using melee and ranged, making both forms much faster to kill.

*The [[Ring of suffering (ri)]] is useful here due to [[Kalphite Queen]] constantly hitting you for high damage, triggering the recoil effect.  Alternatively, the [[Lightbearer]] can give additional follow up special attacks if you are not resetting every kill. Both are generally better than strength rings, as extra defence reduction and recoiled damage add up over both phases.

*It is still recommended to occasionally [[flinch]] the boss when you have to eat or if your supplies are low towards the end of a kill. Step under the boss to limit the amount of times that the [[Kalphite Queen]] can hit. This can be further optimised by using a fast weapon, (such as a blowpipe), followed by a slower heavy hitting weapon, (such as a crossbow) each time you step out from underneath KQ before returning underneath. You are effectively doing 7 cycles of damage vs. the Queen's 4, and will significantly reduce the amount of damage you take throughout the fight.

*An [[Anglerfish]] can be eaten before banking for the fight to boost hitpoints for a slight advantage. 

*Using a Slayer Helm (i) while on task provides a '''far greater bonus to DPS than any other piece of gear'''. If you are struggling, do Slayer tasks until you receive a kalphite task. This will massively improve your chances of success.

